      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone looking for value. While the engine and transmission are functional, the exterior shows some noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior has visible wear on the upholstery. It has been maintained regularly, though it may require some minor upcoming maintenance typical for its age. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
