    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Thanks for stopping by to check out my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and it truly shows\u2014she\u2019s in absolutely gorgeous, showroom-level shape. It honestly feels like stepping back in time when you hop inside. I\u2019ve kept her tucked away in the garage and out of the elements, so she still has \uadf8 sparkle that turns heads at every stoplight. There might be a tiny, tiny mark on the rim if you really go looking with a magnifying glass, but otherwise, she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. I\u2019m only parting with her to make some room in the driveway for my daughter\u2019s first car, so I\u2019m looking for a good home where she'll be appreciated. Come by for a coffee and a look\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
