      "description": "Up for acquisition is an uncompromising example of the legendary S65-powered E92 M3. This isn't your average high-mileage survivor; this is a mechanically optimized specimen. The high-revving 4.0L V8 has been meticulously maintained with treated rod bearings and uprated throttle actuators to negate typical platform vulnerabilities. The M-Double Clutch Transmission (DCT) has been recalibrated with a GTS-spec software flash for lightning-quick shift logic and aggressive rev-matching. The chassis remains laser-straight, featuring zero-deflection bushings and a suspension geometry that delivers surgical turn-in. The exterior retains incredible depth and luster, indicative of a life spent in a climate-controlled environment. From the VANOS system's silent operation to the pristine underbody, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of N/A performance. A turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48900.0,
